data.text:
@smorno Hi! 

I'm sorry that your flight was affected by the strike. The best i can recommend in that case is to contact our customer service. If you can't get through on the phone then i recommend contacting our live-chat. https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards, 
Dennis

@priscillablair Hi! 

I'm sorry if your flight was cancelled. The best i can recommend in that situation is to contact our customer service either by phone or the live chat, as we need to have a look at your booking to see what we can do to solve it for you.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@simonmilligan74 Hi! 

Yes it's usually not a problem to change you to the day before/later if needed. But it depends on the seats available at the time. 

//Best regards, Dennis

@bellafour Hi! 

If you want to have a look at his rebooking options then i recommend that you contact our customer service by phone or the live chat. But we may not be able to rebook his trip for free if his flight is active. https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards, Dennis.

@mattrigney Hi! 

I'm sorry that your bag went missing. The best i can recommend in that situation is to call the arrival service at the airport you arrived at so they can help you look at your case. https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@CEMENT_SHOES69 Hi! 

We usually know if your flight is cancelled a day or two before departure. It's hard to say exactly, but  we will inform you as soon as possible. We can help you look at another flight when your flight is cancelled.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@denis_uu Hi! 

I hope your surgery went well, and i'm sorry that your points expired. But we sadly can't extend/reinstate points after they expire.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@sarah86371623 Hi! 

Okay! They usually send out bags after they arrive to the airport, but i would recommend to still try to get in contact with them via phone just to make sure. We sadly can't help you with your bag from here.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@MatthewHotton Hi! 

I'm sorry that your flight was cancelled. You can send us a compensation request via this link: https://t.co/oKlCwpaMq8

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@Balkandesken Hi! 

We sadly can't say exactly when a flight will be cancelled as it can vary when we get that information. But we will contact you as soon as we know if your flight will be affected.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Mtruesen Hej! 

Tack för din fina kommentar. Vi jobbar på att lösa strejken så fort som möjligt så vi kan erbjuda fler alternativ till våra kunder. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@voxxah Hi! 

I'm sorry that you received an error on the website, and if you had a problem with the chat queue. We sadly have a pretty long queue right now both on phone and on the chat but we are working on it as fast as possible. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@SHvidberg Hej! 

Jag beklagar om ditt bagage vart försenat. Jag förstår att det kan skapa problem. Om ditt bagage var försenat så kan du fylla i informationen nedan så att vi kan fastställa din kompensation: https://t.co/zItZlSXhJp

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Josh___stewart Hi! 

I'm sorry that your bag was delayed. You can send in a complaint and a request for a compensation here: https://t.co/zItZlSXhJp

//Best regards, Dennis.

@lolashrewsbury Hi! 

I'm sorry if you have waited a long time in the queue. We are working on it as fast as possible but there is sadly a long queue right now. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@trishajoshi_ Hi! 

I apologize if your bag was delayed. They are working on sending you your bag as fast as possible. But the best i can recommend is to wait a bit more. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@simonmilligan74 Hi! 

Yes we will be able to rebook you to another flight if yours is cancelled. But it also depends on if there is seats left the same day, so we sadly can't promise anything beforehand. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@JosAbar67689310 Hi! 

I'm sorry if your bag went missing. You will get a message as soon as they find your bag as long as you reported it missing at the airport. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@haseeb1986 Hi! 

I'm sorry if your flight was affected. The app may need to be updated manually. There should be an update button you can press to fix that. Some of our flights are still operating so you were probably rebooked to one of those.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@travelorbust79 Hi! 

I'm sorry that you had to wait so long in queue, we are working on it as fast as possible but the best we can recommend is to wait until an agent responds so they can help you have a look at your alternatives.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@janis_sheppard Hi! 

I'm sorry that your bag went missing. It might be hard to get in contact with them right now, i recommend that you call baggage service at +45 32 32 32 60 so they can help you. We sadly don't have another option for this.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Balkandesken Hi! 

Yes that flight might be affected by the strike if it last that long. It's hard to say right now, but we are doing everything we can to solve this.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@tessissippii Hi @tessissippii, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. Many airports report major baggage delivery delays due to shortage of staff. You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service for more info: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2.
Kind regards, Mikael.

@eimaipharmacist Hello! Flight SK2778 from Athens to Copenhagen will departure at 14:05 local time, today.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@HeidtmannC Hello! For assist with your booking, please contact our customer care on phone or live chat as we are not able to assist with this over social media.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@ian_hardacre Hello! We are very sorry for the inconvenience! If you wish to leave us a complaint, you are welcome to fill in our feedback form, which can be found here: https://t.co/xMt9zSrqJc

Kind regards,
Jenny

@SureshG97194302 Hello! For assist with your missing bag, please contact our baggage service in Copenhagen on number +45 32 32 30 60, Opening Hours on phone: Monday- Friday 09-16, Saturday-Sunday: 09-14 Scandinavian time.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@euro_kip If the boarding pass is not available for digital download, please proceed to the airport and check in manually there.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@travelorbust79 Hello! We are very sorry for the long waiting times to our customer service at the moment. You can contact us either on phone or on our live chat. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Jenny

@marcnelles Hello! We are very sorry for the inconvenience! For assist, please contact our customer service on phone or live chat. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Jenny

@euro_kip Hello! You can see your booking by inserting your booking reference on the website under "my bookings". For some destinations, online check in is not available. If you fly with us the whole way, and during the same day, the bags will go all the way directly.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@misssamantham Hello! Our Go pro ticket to/from the US is freely rebookable and fully refundable yes. Though rebooking to other origin/destination can only be changed to other airports within USA.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@FunkeMama Hello! Ice skates are allowed in carry on, on our flights yes.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@samanthalzu Hello! Unfortunatly we are not able to assist with this over social media. Please contact our customer service on phone or live chat. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Jenny

@CJinPinstripes Hello! Should your booking be affected by the strike, we will immediately try to find an alternative for your flight automatically. If the new alternative is not suitable, or no alternative has been given, please contact our customer service for assist. 

Kind regards
Jenny

@dmnicholson Hello! We are very sorry for the inconvenience! For assist with your missing bag, please contact our baggage service staff in Dublin on number +353 180 80 381.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@TTarahealy Hello! Unfortunatly we are not able to assist with this over social media. Please contact our customer service on phone or live chat for further assist. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Jenny

@Desiree_Pultrum Hello! If your case is concerning a compensation claim, you can contact our customer care on care@sas.se for further assist with your claim. You can also contact our customer service on phone or live chat and continue to one of our live collegues.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@Ghada_AJ11 Hello! For assist, you can contact us on phone or live chat. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Warm regards,
Jenny

@iddibhai Hello! A full refund can not be aqcuired proactively unfortunatly, but we do offer a free rebooking if your departure date is between 06 July - 11 July 2022, and can be rebooked to other SK flights, maximum 360 days ahead in time. 

Warm regards,
Jenny

@StyrmirBar Hello! Please contact our customer service on phone or live chat so we can have a look at your booking and the refund. Contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Warm regards,
Jenny

@SimonDyhr Hej!
När ni anmält ert bagage försvunnet påbörjas denna sökning direkt. Efter att bagaget lokaliserats blir ni informerade gällande leverans. För vidare frågor som status eller uppdateringar, bör ni vända er till Bagage Service: https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM

Bästa hälsningar, Angelica

@RobertSulcas Hi @RobertSulcas, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@HmellisaM Hi @HmellisaM, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@Amie__Farrell Hi @Amie__Farrell, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@TuttleAlena Hi, 
If your luggage is delayed, you need to contact the luggage service at the airport which was your final destination for information. You can find the telephone numbers via this link https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM
//Henrik

@e_extremena Hi,
If your refund can not be processed due to the bank account being inactive you will receive an email with a request to submit your bank details.
Kind Regards, Rebecca

@Quin7066 Hi Quinny, so sorry to hear about your luggage. You can read more about your rights at: https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM
Since your luggage has been lost for more than 21 days I'd advice you to make a claim with our Customer Care dept. at: https://t.co/zItZlSXhJp
Kind Regards, Rebecca

@BiaCuri Hello! 
We can not assist with specific matters over Twitter. You are welcome to contact our support and we will help you with your case. You can find our contacts here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Anja!

@wahl_kathrin Hej!
Vi kan dessvärre inte assistera med ombokningsärenden över facebook. Vänligen vänta kvar i samtalet så kommer en av mina kollegor att hjälpa dig så snart som möjligt. 

Tack för att du kontaktar oss, hälsningar Anja!

@Catwys Hello
You are welcome to apply for compensation for the lost baggage via our customer care department. You can contact them via this link: https://t.co/cXegpq56aG and select "general complaint or compliment".

Kind regards, Anja!

@MethodLead Hello
SAS as an airline does not require a test or a vaccination certificate for the traveler to travel with us, but the staff at check in will check your travel documents and any test if the country you are traveling to requires this.

Kind regards, Anja!

@Salahnamaaaaaa Hi, If the luggage weighs more than 23kg, you will have to pay for overweight at the airport

Kind regards,
Henrik

@Salahnamaaaaaa Hello! Unfortunatly, it is not possible to merge 2 passengers baggage allowances. If the luggage is bigger than 158 cm in total, you need to contact our customer service so we can add it as bulky baggage in the booking. 

Kind regards,
Jenny

@Troj07 Hello! We still do not have any information as to if we need to cancel flights due to a potential strike. If you wish to see the status of your flights, please visit https://t.co/Zq7JSjFRk9 

Kind regards,
Jenny

@MxHedroom You can buy carry on at the airport also absolutly!

Kind regards,
Jenny

@rumbosysuspiros Hello! We are truly sorry for the inconvenience! For assist with your lost luggage, please contact our baggage department in Oslo on number +47 64 81 27 00 or visit our baggage department on the airport for easier handling.

Kind regards,
Jenny

@Ronny_Larsson Hej! Vi ber verkligen om ursäkt för besväret! För hjälp med att lägga in passinformation och first night stay, var vänlig kontakta oss på telefon +46 770 727 727 så hjälper vi dig att lägga in det i bokningen.

Med vänliga hälsningar,
Jenny

@Roarsbash Hello! We are truly sorry for the inconvenience! For assist with your booking, please contact our customer service on messenger, live chat or phone. Our contact information can be found here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Jenny
